text: Lee-Anne Keet (born 12 October 1982) is a South African water polo player. She competed for the South Africa women's national water polo team in the 2009 World Aquatics Championships, and 2013 World Aquatics Championships. == References == ==Other websites== *sport-mad-lee-anne-home-from-ireland *Lee- Anne+Keet *FINA World Championships Women Water Polo Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:South African water polo players
